body.name: Cotopaxi Cubos Travel Cubes - Del Dia - One of a Kind!
features: THIS IS ONE CUBE OF RANDOM COLOR SELECTION - ONE OF A KIND! Each Del Dia product is made proudly in the Philippines by an employee who has total creative control over the pack's colorway. No two are the same! We'll choose a pack for you at random. Be prepared for a total surprise!
Made with repurposed materials and a wrap-around zipper for easy access, these simple organizers store clothes, toiletries, and other must-have items.
Mesh side panels provide ample ventilation, while a top grab handle makes for easy carrying or pulling out of your pack.
Durable yet lightweight construction made with repurposed nylon and mesh.
Wrap-around zipper for quick access. Mesh side panels boost breathability. Top handle for easy carry.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Cubos Travel Cube - Del Día Whether you’re road-tripping somewhere for the weekend or are living out of a backpack for two months, organization is key, and our travel cubes keep all of your essentials in order. Made with repurposed materials and a wrap-around zipper for easy access, these simple organizers store clothes, toiletries, and other must-have items. Mesh side panels provide ample ventilation, while a top grab handle makes for easy carrying or pulling out of your pack. Durable yet lightweight construction made with repurposed nylon and meshWrap-around zipper for quick accessMesh side panels boost breathabilityTop handle for easy carry ONE OF A KIND Our Del Dia products take material repurposing to the next level, using smaller batches of excess material than our Repurposed Collection. Employees at our factory in the Philippines select rolls of excess fabric. Using these remnant materials, expert designers and sewers mix and match fabrics and components (e.g., zippers, zipper pulls, buckles, and thread) to their liking. The result? Waste-saving, one-of-a-kind products, with a built-in connection between our team of designers, sewers, and you.

Why We Built This & Why It's Different Sometimes a bag needs extra organization. Why not organize in color? The Cubos Travel Cube is made from 100% remnant materials that could have gone to a landfill. Instead, we use these materials to create one-of-a-kind packs and accessories.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 9, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Quality Packing Cubes
reviews.reviewText: These are awesome for travel organization!The materials and quality seem to be great, and the colors of these make them stand out compared to other options on the market.The mesh on the sides is great for items that may not the dried fully like a swimsuit.They are very simple packing cubes but can fold up really small when they are not in use.Overall I will be buying more of these for future adventures.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 17, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good quality and design
reviews.reviewText: Great quality, love the colors. My son feels so special getting to pick his clothes out of the packing cubes when we travel

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 25, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect for traveling!
reviews.reviewText: We use these bags in our RV. Perfect for traveling.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 27, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I was able to pack a weeks worth of bulky sweaters among other stuff in a 26 L backpack. They’re so cute too. Love the colors they make me feel happier. I really want a cotapaxi backpack now to match.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 23, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Like them but
reviews.reviewText: I just wish they were a little bit bigger the smallest one is too small for clothes but too big and unstructured to keep in my workbag. I love the brand and the quality is great, but none of these is large enough to really work as luggage separators. At best toiletries. But I barely want to do that because I'm worried the lighter fabrics will stain with makeup.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 28, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Very good, ease to use and very practical

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Picture show three. YOU GET ONE.
reviews.reviewText: The bag is great, but beware! There are three bags in the photo, the title is plural but only one bag arrives at your door, hence the low price. The one star review is for saying “bags” instead of “bag” and the photo with three items in it instead of one. The bag itself is fine.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 13, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Advertisement is Misleading
reviews.reviewText: I ordered this as a gift for my sister. It is well-made, but the photo in the advertisement showed three cubes in different sizes. When I went to add to my cart, it did not have me choose a size, so all along, I believed that I was getting all three. She received the package and there's only one. Disappointing. The ad should say, choose S, M or L AND when you select to buy, it should indicate the sizes.

reviews.reviewTitle: Produit de grande qualité, tel que sur la photo
reviews.reviewText: Très heureuse de mon achat qui comprenait l’ensemble de 3 trousses de voyage Cotopaxi.Identique à la photo et superbe qualité. Il y a plusieurs produits sur Amazon, si vous voulez l’ensemble de 3, c’est important de choisir le cube bundle.

Me encanta la marca Cotopaxi.Pero este cubo que lo venden cómo tamaño mediano.Si me decepciono mucho porque es muy pequeño.Como para ropa interior ó calcetines.Pero por el precio mejor comprar otros cubos que traen más tamaños y que sean de compresión por el mismo precio de uno solo.
Contrairement à ce que certains puissent dire, j'ai bien reçu les 3 sacs et j'en suis très satisfait.
Thought I was buying the set of three as pictured. It is a single organizer. Good quality, just misleading.
Very cute packing cube, and always unique, but the product description says 2 items (presumably the same size cubes) for the price and I only received one.
